{"tid":1911368,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"衞生防護中心 仍在調查北角佛堂群組個案病毒源頭","createTime":"2020-03-05T09:33:27.000Z","updateTime":"2020-03-05T09:42:15.000Z","uid":41818,"like":0,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":2,"replies":[{"pid":"0c5eec064147a9a156c04be8fdfa835bb8651d42","tid":1911368,"uid":41818,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-05T09:33:27.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://newsstatic.rthk.hk/images/mfile_1512665_1_L_20200305171758.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnewsstatic.rthk.hk%2Fimages%2Fmfile_1512665_1_L_20200305171758.jpg&h=19e097eb&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n張竹君說，佛堂曾經舉行由僧人帶領的儀式，包括內地人及曾經到過內地的人士。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n衞生防護中心傳染病處主任張竹君表示，仍在調查北角「福慧精舍」佛堂的病毒源頭，仍未有真正的結果，不排除任何一個群組有機會是病源的可能。<br />\n<br />\n張竹君說，佛堂在上月5日及6日曾經舉行由僧人帶領的儀式，包括內地人及曾經到過內地的人士。<br />\n<br />\n根據佛堂資料，有7人是由外地請來，已找到其中1名曾經去過上海的人，當時亦有頭痛，被送到東區醫院接受檢查，化驗結果是陰性，其他人士仍在尋找中，未知道他們曾到過甚麼地方，亦未能確定病源會否與他們有關。<br />\n<br />\n被問到曾到過內地的男法師為何不是病源，張竹君說，居住在佛堂的男法師一直無病徵，未肯定是否早前已感染至最近才發病。<br />\n<br />\n她解釋，暫時將佛堂群組最早發病的個案視為源頭個案，是方便中心計算，並非已確定最早發病的個案就是源頭。 <br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1512665-20200305.htm?spTabChangeable=0\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1512665-20200305.htm%3FspTabChangeable%3D0&d=%2BwrRK7ySmiC6A5TqlPyaq4GpPR2DWAUw81xbwDiv9SI%3D&h=1c4b713b\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1512665-20200305.htm%3FspTabChangeable%3D0&h=42d70ea6\" target=\"_blank\">https://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1512665-20200305.htm?spTabChangeable=0</a>"},{"pid":"d01fe048b0f3038ae50ee03919f938e001f2fe96","tid":1911368,"uid":207543,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-05T09:42:15.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/HAkR4am.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FHAkR4am.jpg&h=5fb9bb1d&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/PiTPQQm.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FPiTPQQm.jpg&h=c4011e8d&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n#8Mar #將軍澳 #悼念會 #周同學<br />\n【梓樂悼念會】<br />\n日期 : 3月8日 (日)<br />\n時間 : 19:30 (20:09分默哀)<br />\n地點 : 將軍澳 尚十<br />\n*請自備蠟燭鮮花 , 及戴口罩<br />\nSource : <a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/photo.php?fbid=3018832514817307&amp;set=gm.1240521269478455&amp;type=3\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2Fphoto.php%3Ffbid%3D3018832514817307%26set%3Dgm.1240521269478455%26type%3D3&d=%2BwrRK7ySmiC6A5TqlPyaq4GpPR2DWAUw81xbwDiv9SI%3D&h=68ec59f5\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.facebook.com/photo.php?fbid=3018832514817307&amp;set=gm.1240521269478455&amp;type=3</a>"}]}